41:03.261 --> 41:04.963
Bye-bye.

41:05.030 --> 41:06.665
Come on, baby.

41:06.732 --> 41:10.702
(whimsical classical music
playing)

41:13.438 --> 41:15.941
(sighs)

41:18.009 --> 41:19.678
(chuckles)

41:24.449 --> 41:27.085
(turn signal clicking)

41:30.388 --> 41:33.024
RICHARD:
Going to the car show
and looking at the minivans

41:33.091 --> 41:36.862
