we're finding now

41:46.404 --> 41:49.507
is that most
advertising dollars
are migrating online.

41:49.575 --> 41:52.544
(cell phone ringing)

41:52.611 --> 41:54.412
Is that you?

41:54.479 --> 41:56.815
(ringing continues)

41:56.882 --> 41:58.049
It's me.

41:58.116 --> 41:59.618
