42:27.646 --> 42:30.849
(whispering):
Okay, I promise.

42:30.916 --> 42:33.785
Will you come with me to get my
stuff out of Teddy's apartment?

42:33.852 --> 42:35.887
Didn't you hear me tell you
I'm in a meeting?

42:35.954 --> 42:36.922
Not today,

42:36.988 --> 42:38.123
