42:38.189 --> 42:39.357
Fine.

42:39.424 --> 42:40.759
Okay? I got to go now.

42:40.826 --> 42:41.960
Have a good meeting.

42:43.061 --> 42:45.897
LANDIS:
Oh, and what were your plans?

42:45.964 --> 42:46.898
Three kids?

42:46.965 --> 42:48.266
LANDIS:
Yeah, could be better.

42:48.333 --> 42:50.268
(door closes)

42:50.335 --> 42:52.203
Small family emergency.

42:52.270 --> 42:54.272
