42:54.339 --> 42:56.274
(car horns honking)

42:59.244 --> 43:01.246
RICHARD:
All right,
so where's this guy live?

43:01.312 --> 43:02.948
'Cause I got things
to do.

43:03.014 --> 43:05.483
Shuttle's in,
like, 45 minutes.

43:05.550 --> 43:06.918
Shuttle?

43:06.985 --> 43:09.454
Wh-What are you
talking about, shuttle?

43:09.520 --> 43:10.689
To D.C.

43:10.756 --> 43:12.624
Remember I told you,
we have a place there,

43:12.691 --> 43:15.593
