with you to D.C.

43:18.363 --> 43:19.998
You promised.

43:20.065 --> 43:22.467
I didn't promise to go
with you to another state.

43:22.533 --> 43:24.836
It's not a state,
it's a district.

43:24.903 --> 43:27.138
It's, like, a
30-minute flight.

43:27.205 --> 43:29.741
You must be
out of your fucking mind

43:29.808 --> 43:33.011
if you think I'm getting
on a plane to Washington D.C.

43:33.078 --> 43:35.847
to go to some guy's house
to get your shit!

43:45.523 --> 43:46.424
GEORGE:
Richard?

43:46.491 --> 43:47.759
Richard, yeah.

43:47.826 --> 43:49.928
