43:51.296 --> 43:52.463
No, no, no, don't worry.

43:52.530 --> 43:53.665
I'll be there.

43:53.732 --> 43:55.533
Yeah, something
just came up.

43:55.600 --> 43:56.835
Look, just get here, okay?

43:56.902 --> 43:58.403
