when you get here.

44:04.542 --> 44:07.112
You're a good liar.

44:07.178 --> 44:09.547
Listen, we're getting
on the 1:00 shuttle,

44:09.614 --> 44:10.648
not a moment later, okay?

44:10.716 --> 44:12.250
'Cause I got
a meeting at 3:00.

44:12.317 --> 44:14.019
Okay.

44:23.494 --> 44:25.663
(siren blaring)

44:28.967 --> 44:29.835
NIKKI:
Right here.

44:29.901 --> 44:30.969
Here?
Uh-huh.

44:31.036 --> 44:32.670
What are all these
cops doing here?

44:32.738 --> 44:34.706
Oh, it's kind of
a crazy neighborhood.

44:34.773 --> 44:35.974
Something's always
going down.

44:36.041 --> 44:37.843
We'll be right back.
Okay.

44:37.909 --> 44:39.945
