Open up in there!

44:49.888 --> 44:51.356
In Miami, I lived
with his brother.

44:51.422 --> 44:52.223
That's where
I met him.

44:52.290 --> 44:53.725
Wait a minute,
you lived with a guy,

44:53.792 --> 44:56.261
