I want pancakes.

45:00.665 --> 45:01.900
We're in.

45:09.674 --> 45:12.110
All right,
now that we're in,

45:12.177 --> 45:13.745
I want you to
get your shit

45:13.812 --> 45:15.280
and let's get
out of here.

45:15.346 --> 45:17.749
I'm just gonna grab
a few dresses, some shoes,

45:17.816 --> 45:18.716
and then we'll go.

45:18.784 --> 45:20.218
Okay.

45:20.285 --> 45:21.486
Thank you.

45:21.552 --> 45:23.454
Forget "Thank you,"
just hurry up.

45:27.926 --> 45:29.394
Teddy's doing
pretty good.

45:29.460 --> 45:30.328
Mm-hmm.

45:34.532 --> 45:37.068
(sirens in distance)

45:40.338 --> 45:42.908
You were on the math team
in high school?

45:42.974 --> 45:45.176
For two years. Why?

45:45.243 --> 45:46.211
I don't know.

45:46.277 --> 45:48.880
