solving a problem.

45:48.947 --> 45:51.817
My Ferretti sweater.

45:51.883 --> 45:54.820
I had no idea
where this was.

46:01.827 --> 46:03.294
Richard Cooper's office.

46:03.361 --> 46:04.362
Hi, Brenda.

46:06.231 --> 46:07.532
Hey, somebody
around here's

46:07.598 --> 46:09.500
