48:06.284 --> 48:07.452
No, no.

48:07.518 --> 48:09.354
No, no, no!

48:11.722 --> 48:13.658
Could you hurry up?

48:18.930 --> 48:21.967
(woman speaking indistinctly
over intercom)

48:24.202 --> 48:26.337
(metal detector beeping)

48:28.806 --> 48:30.641
(high-pitched
electrical whining)

48:34.845 --> 48:38.116
I don't care about "Thriller."

48:38.183 --> 48:41.886
What kind of grown man
