48:41.953 --> 48:44.855
He'll never babysit my kids.

48:44.922 --> 48:46.757
Look, we don't have all day.

48:46.824 --> 48:48.193
LANDIS:
I'm-I'm sorry, Mr. Yuni.

48:48.259 --> 48:49.827
